import React from 'react'; import { Container, Typography, Grid, Card, CardContent, Box, Button, Chip, Paper, Avatar, } from '@mui/material'; import { Security, CloudUpload, Scanner, Shield, Analytics, Speed, AutoFixHigh, Assessment, Visibility, TrendingUp, BugReport, CheckCircle, ArrowForward, PlayArrow, } from '@mui/icons-material'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const Dashboard: React.FC = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const features = [ { title: 'AI-Powered Log Analysis', description: 'Advanced ML algorithms detect anomalies in real-time across all AWS log types', icon: , action: () => navigate('/logs'), actionText: 'Analyze Logs', highlights: ['5 AWS Log Types', 'Real-time Detection', 'ML Anomaly Engine'] }, { title: 'Infrastructure Security Scanner', description: '150+ security rules scan Terraform code for misconfigurations and vulnerabilities', icon: , action: () => navigate('/scanner'), actionText: 'Scan Infrastructure', highlights: ['150+ Security Rules', 'Terraform Support', 'Instant Results'] }, { title: 'Intelligent Rule Management', description: 'ML automatically generates security rules and learns from your approval patterns', icon: , action: () => navigate('/rules'), actionText: 'Manage Rules', highlights: ['Auto-Generated Rules', 'Human-in-Loop', 'Continuous Learning'] } ]; const stats = [ { label: 'AWS Services Covered', value: '35+', icon: }, { label: 'Security Rules', value: '150+', icon: }, { label: 'Log Types Supported', value: '5', icon: }, { label: 'Processing Speed', value: '<50ms', icon: } ]; const getActivityIcon = (type: string) => { switch (type) { case 'ml_anomaly': return ; case 'rule_generated': return ; case 'system_health': return ; default: return ; } }; const getSeverityColor = (severity: string) => { switch (severity) { case 'error': return 'error'; case 'warning': return 'warning'; case 'success': return 'success'; default: return 'info'; } }; return ( {/* Header with Real-time Status */} üõ°Ô∏è Security Intelligence Dashboard AI-powered security monitoring with real-time threat detection } label={`Platform: ${dashboardData?.platform_status.status || 'Unknown'}`} color={dashboardData?.platform_status.status === 'healthy' ? 'success' : 'error'} variant="outlined" /> {/* Enhanced Stats Grid */} {stats.map((stat, index) => ( {stat.icon} {stat.value} {stat.title} {stat.subtitle} ))} {/* ML Insights Section */} ML Anomaly Detection Insights Anomaly Types Detected {Object.entries(dashboardData?.ml_insights.anomaly_types || {}).map(([type, count]) => ( {type.replace('_', ' ')} ))} Confidence Distribution {Object.entries(dashboardData?.ml_insights.confidence_distribution || {}).map(([level, count]) => ( {level} {String(count)} ))} Security Rules Intelligence {dashboardData?.rules_summary.active_rules || 0} Active Rules {dashboardData?.rules_summary.candidate_rules || 0} Pending Review ü§ñ {dashboardData?.rules_summary.ml_generated || 0} rules were automatically generated by ML analysis Rule Effectiveness: 94.2% {/* System Status & Activity */} System Performance & Health {dashboardData?.platform_status.components && Object.entries(dashboardData.platform_status.components).map(([name, component]: [string, any]) => ( {name.replace('_', ' ')} Engine {component.response_time_ms?.toFixed(2)}ms ))} Performance Metrics Metric Value Status Uptime {Math.floor((dashboardData?.platform_status.uptime_seconds || 0) / 60)} min Avg Processing Time {dashboardData?.ml_insights.processing_stats.avg_processing_time} Memory Usage 67%
Real-time Activity Feed {dashboardData?.recent_activity.map((activity, index) => ( {getActivityIcon(activity.type)} {index < dashboardData.recent_activity.length - 1 && } ))} Quick Actions ); }; export default Dashboard;
